quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  2,189,"HiЙ“e naamno-maa fii darorЙ—e lebbi, wi'u: \"ЖЉin ko waqaЕ‹tinanayЙ—i yimЙ“e e fii hajju\".Dewal ngal wonaali nde ngardaЕ‹ton cuuЙ—i Й—in immorde ka Й“abbe majji, si ko woni dewal ngal: ko on gomЙ—uЙ—o.Ngardanee cuuЙ—i Й—in ka dame majji.Hulon Allah,belajo'o on malete"
  2,190,"HaЙ“ee fii laawol Alla ngol Й“en haЙ“ooЙ“e on, wata on jaggitu. Pellet, Alla yiЙ—aa jaggitooЙ“e Й“en"
  2,191,"wareeЙ“e nokku kala ka tawЙ—on Й“e, yaltineeЙ“e nokku ka Й“e yaltiniri on: ko geddi Й—in Й“uri mawnude e dii haЙ“ugol ngol. Wata on haЙ“uЙ“e ka Misiide HormaЕ‹teere haa Й“e haЙ“a on e mayre. Si Й“e haЙ“ii on haЙ“ee Й“e. Ko wano nii woni njoЙ“di heeferЙ“e Й“en"
  2,192,"Si Й“e haЙ—itike, pellet, Alla ko O Hafroowo HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yumeende"
  2,193,"HaЙ“ee Й“e haa nokku ka laatotaako fitina, diina kan laatanoo Alla. Si Й“e haЙ—itike, haray jaggitere alanaa si wanaa Й“en tooГ±ooЙ“e"
  2,194,"Si Й“e haЙ“ii on e lewru hormaЕ‹teeru, haЙ“ee Й“e e lewru hormaЕ‹teeru, horminaaЙ—i Й—in ko yottondirtee Й—um. On mo jaggiti e mo'on jaggitee e dow makko yeru kon ko o jaggiti e dow mooЙ—on. Hulee Alla anndon pellet Alla no wonndi Й“en gomЙ—uЙ“e"
  2,195,"WiЕ‹tee e fii laawol Alla, wata on bugor juuЙ—e mon Й—en faade e halakuyee. MoЖґЖґinee, pellet Alla no YiЙ—i moЖґЖґinayЙ“e Й“en"
  2,196,"Timminiree hajju ngun e 'omra on fii Alla. Si on sakkaama: fawike on ittugol kon ko newii e kirse, wata on femmbu ko'e mon Й—en haa kirse Й—en yottoo nokku majje. On tawЙ—o e mo'on ko Г±awЙ—o maa lorra no ka hoore makko, ko soktorgol: koorka, maa sadaqa maa dammol. Si on wonii e hoolaare, on mo dakmitori 'omra on haa ka hajju: fawike mo ittugol kon ko newii e kirse. Mo heЙ“aali, ko hoorugol balЙ—e tati ka hajju e jeeЙ—iЙ—i si on ruttike; Й—en ko sappo timmuЙ—e. Ko jaЕ‹taa koo, ko fii on tawЙ—o Й“eynguure mun nden laataaki hoЙ—uЙ“e ka Misiide hormaЕ‹te. Hulee Alla, anndon pellet Alla ko saЙ—tuЙ—o lepte"
  2,197,"Hajju ngun:ko lebbi anndaaЙ—i. Mo anniyike e nder majji hajju,renndugol alaa,wanaa faasoqingol wanaa kadi yeddondiro ka hajju.Kala ku gollugЙ—on e moЖґЖґere, Allah no Anndi Й—um.YooЙ“ee,ko Й“uri moЖґЖґude e njooЙ“a,ko gomЙ—al. Hulee Lam yo joomiraaЙ“e haqqillaaji"
  2,198,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on nde Й—aЙ“Й“oton arsike immorde e Joomi mo'on. Si on iwtii 'Aarafaat, JaЕ‹tee innde Alla ka nokku horminannde. JaЕ‹toron Mo wano O fewniri on non, hari on laatinoke ado muuЙ—um ko on jeyaaЙ“e e majjuЙ“e"
  2,199,"Refti yahron ka yimЙ“e Й“en yahri Й—on, InsinanoЙ—on Alla. Pellet Alla ko YaafotooЙ—o HuuЙ“uЙ—o-yurmeende"
  2,200,"Si on gaynii dewe hajju mon ngun, jaЕ‹toree innde Alla wano jaЕ‹torton baabiraaЙ“e mo'on, maa ko Й“uri Й—um tiiЙ—ude. No e yimЙ“e Й“en wi'ooЙ“e: \"Joomi amen Rokku men ka aduna\", alanaa mo ka laakara geЙ“al-moЖґЖґal"
  2,201,"No e maЙ“Й“e wi'ooЙ“e: Joomi amen, okku min moyyere aduna e laakara, ndanndaa min lebte jayngol"
  2,202,"ЖЃen Й—on, no woodani Й“e geЙ“al-moЖґЖґal e kon ko Й“e faggitii. Alla ko YaawuЙ—o hasboore"